Placeholder for adding a new cold brew recipe
This will be now used for 'French Cafe au Lait' recipe
Gather the ingredients.
Into a large cup, pour equal parts of strong hot coffee and steamed milk, reserving the foam.
Stir
Spoon reserved foam on top and serve hot.
If you're artistic, you might want to try your hand at using the steamed milk to create latte art, or simply give it a sprinkle of cinnamon.